1. All URLs should be of form *.htm
2. only lower cases are allowed in urls.
3. All Classes Should be Commented with Date, Author, Purpose and Shoud follow Java Conventions
4. All Methods Should follow, Creation Date Author, Purpose, Logical Steps if any, List of Modifications and modifier
5  USER ROLES :
                ROLE_SUPERADMIN
                ROLE_ORGANIZATION_ADMIN
                ROLE_ORGANIZATION_MASTER
                ROLE_USER
                
6. The system wont have Anonymous Users+
7. Intial Module Divisions is User, Organization, Project, Budget, Tasks, TimeCard, Vacation
8. All Time Card Related Activities like Organization,Project,Tasks,Budget etc will be under timecard package



